              market data, news, and trading tools to professionals worldwide.
            </p>
            <h3>Technologies</h3>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">React</span>
              <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo">
            <img src={`${base}images/bloomberg.svg`} alt="Bloomberg" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </li>

