              <a class="tag" href="https://jquery.com/" target="_blank">Jquery</a>
              <a class="tag" href="https://www.mysql.com/" target="_blank">Mysql</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo">
            <img src={`${base}images/famefitness/famefit-cal.png`} />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </li>

      <li class="element">
        <div class="time">
          <time class="label">Jan 2008</time>
        </div>
        <div class="contents">
          <div class="description">
            <h2>Vehicle Fits</h2>
            <p>Aftermarket parts lookup tool</p>
            <p>
              I initially founded Vehicle Fits to provide a year/make/model
              lookup tool, it quickly expanded to a generalized fitments tool
              used by multiple vertical industries.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>a dynamic schema system / custom fields engine</li>
              <li>
                industry specific plugins like wheel & tire fitments, bolt
                patterns tools, bulk import tools, etc..
              </li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Technologies</h3>
            <div class="tags">
              <a class="tag" href="http://php.net/" target="_blank">PHP</a>
